lsusb
lists usb devices, -t arg for tree view

watch -d lsusb
lists usb devices and checks for updated every 2 seconds, highlighting changes

lspci
lists pci bus

lscpu
self explanatory at this point

lsblk
bulk storage devices

hwinfo (may not be pre-installed)
better to pipe this into a text file, huge info dump

inxi -Fxz
detailed hardware information